==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spiritous
<hw>Spir"it*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Spirituous</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Like spirit; refined;
defecated; pure.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>More refined, more <qex>spirituous</qex> and pure.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Ardent; active.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spiritousness</ent>⟦br⟧
